# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# agents/.gitignore
#
# Anything under agents/ that's regenerable from the scripts here.
# Paths in this file are relative to agents/.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

# ---------- agents/graphify/ ----------
#
# Tracked under graphify/:
#   *.py *.sh README.md .gitignore               (tooling)
#   <package>-module-level/MODULE_RELATIONSHIPS*.md   (text Mermaid for diff/PR)
#
# Everything else is regenerable. Strategy: ignore every subdirectory
# of graphify/ by default, then re-include the *-module-level/ ones
# so the committed .md files inside are tracked.

graphify/*/
!graphify/*-module-level/

# Within those re-included dirs, ignore the generated HTML + per-run
# graphify-out/ subdir.
graphify/*-module-level/*.html
graphify/*-module-level/graphify-out/

# ---------- agents/codebase-map/ ----------
#
# *.md files are LLM-enriched narratives — tracked.
# *.json sidecars are regenerable from the mapper — ignored.

codebase-map/*.json

# ---------- agents/api-flow/ ----------
#
# TypeScript build outputs + npm artifacts.

api-flow/dist/
api-flow/node_modules/
api-flow/*.tsbuildinfo

# ---------- agents/schema/ ----------
#
# Schema diagram is regenerated from backend/prisma/schema.prisma by
# the build script. No content here is hand-written.

schema/

# ---------- agents/HUB.html ----------
#
# The unified hub is generated from whatever views are currently
# available. Always regenerate; never commit.

HUB.html
